{{Natural language} The entry and doActivity Behaviors of a State
must conform to all the Triggers of Transitions that might cause the
State to be entered. The exit Behavior of a State must conform to all
the Triggers of Transitions that might cause the State to be exited.
The effect and guard Behaviors of an outgoing Transition of a State
must conform to all the Triggers of the Transition. (Note that only
Transitions outgoing from a State may have Triggers.)}
